  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the things did change after that, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, of course-- as I said, I did think Poland is strong.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very patriotic, in fact, [LAUGHS] and very emotional.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they did sing the Polish national hymn, I always remember having tears in my eyes, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somehow I was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both, both.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as I said, I did think Poland is strong for some reason.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the first German tanks [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] entered Krakow, and I did see it, that was, to me, like people from the other planet.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was so newly equipped, and so strong, and so overpowering.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so [SIGHS] then I understood, and I felt how weak Poland was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the bad--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
